        "content": "<style>\n.join-the-community {\nborder-radius: 99px;\nbackground: #121212;\npadding: 8.918px 32px;\nheight: 56px;\ncolor: #FFF;\nfont-size: 18px;\nfont-weight: 700;\nmargin-top: 24px;\n}\nul {\ncolor: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.60);\nfont-size: 16px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 24px;\n}\n</style>\n\nJoin our community to\n<ul>\n<li>Ask questions after the live stream</li>\n<li>Share prints, workflows, and real results</li>\n<li>Learn from other Procolored users worldwide</li>\n</ul>",
